A BILL ENTITLED
1 AN ACT concerning
2 Evidence – Interception of Oral Communications – Fair Housing Testing
3 FOR the purpose of providing that it is lawful for a person to intercept an oral
4 communication if the person is working as a fair housing tester for a certain fair
5 housing testing program under certain circumstances; and generally relating to
6 electronic surveillance.
