11 (c) (12) (I) IT IS LAWFUL UNDER THIS SUBTITLE FOR A PERSON TO
12 INTERCEPT AN ORAL COMMUNICATION IF:
13 1. THE PERSON IS WORKING AS A FAIR HOUSING TESTER
14 FOR A FAIR HOUSING TESTING PROGRAM OPERATED BY:
15 A. THE FEDERAL GOVERNMENT;
16 B. THE STATE;
17 C. A LOCAL GOVERNMENT; OR
18 D. A NONPROFIT CIVIL RIGHTS ORGANIZATION;
