20 AND
21 3. THE INTERCEPTION IS BEING MADE FOR THE
22 PURPOSE OF OBTAINING EVIDENCE OF A FAIR HOUSING VIOLATION UNDER
23 FEDERAL, STATE, OR LOCAL LAW.
