25 PARAGRAPH, NO PART OF THE CONTENTS OF THE INTERCEPTED COMMUNICATION
26 AND NO EVIDENCE DERIVED THEREFROM MAY BE RECEIVED IN EVIDENCE IN ANY
27 TRIAL, HEARING, OR OTHER PROCEEDING IN OR BEFORE ANY COURT, GRAND JURY,
28 DEPARTMENT, OFFICER, AGENCY, REGULATORY BODY, LEGISLATIVE COMMITTEE,
29 OR OTHER AUTHORITY OF THE STATE OR A POLITICAL SUBDIVISION OF THE STATE.
30 (III) THE CONTENTS OF AN INTERCEPTED ORAL
31 COMMUNICATION MADE IN ACCORDANCE WITH SUBPARAGRAPH (I) OF THIS

